title: Settings activity (#8)
message:
Settings activity (#8)

* Allow vertical scrolling in the settings activity

Given that the activity uses the CoordinatorLayout, and following the android indications [CoordinatorLayout](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/support/design/widget/CoordinatorLayout.html) the ViewGroup was wrong -RelativeLayout- it must be a scrollable view, for instance NestedScrollView.

Avoid using absolute values for dimensions for the scrollable content

* Showcase of the CoordinatorLayout capabilities

Added an attribute to the toolbar element so that it is appreciated how the CoordinatorLayout works on the toolbar

title: Version 1.5
message:
Version 1.5 

Added settings menu, you can now change the colors of the titlebar, text, and floating buttons!
You can also choose the length of the title for the notes.

Fixed the helper note by removing it and added help to menu options.
Edited so notes only show first 25 characters in list view menu.
Also added Settings menu option, will add more details, but it will be able to change the user's colors of text, titlebars, etc...
